it.eng.qbe.model.structure
Interface IModelStructure

All Superinterfaces:
IModelObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
FilteredModelStructure, ModelStructure
public interface IModelStructure
extends IModelObject

represent the structure of the data exposed by a IDataSource. Because a data source can be built also upon different data models (i.e. CompositeQbe) an IModelStructure can contains multiple structure, one for each model contained in the composite data source. Each structure is represented trough a collection of tree hierarchies identified by the name of the model it maps.

getModelNames

java.util.Set<java.lang.String> getModelNames()
Returns:
The names of all the models managed by this structure. To each model is associated an independent collection of tree hierarchies of IModelObjects identified by the name of the model it maps.
